snippet.title: Diablo IV Official Cinematic Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description:
An all new cinematic trailer for Diablo IV was shown during the 2022 Game Awards, featuring Blizzard's signature epic cinematic. Diablo IV is expected to release June 6, 2023.

#Diablo4 #Diablo
